{"tid":1358482,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"班小學雞明唔明咩係不合作運動？","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T01:13:32.000Z","uid":267337,"like":6,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3fde318a9995ba92a7a8b4cad594c085953ee7","tid":1358482,"uid":267337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"我唔知依班係咩人<br />\n但佢地宣稱自己進行「不合作運動」<br />\n我無辦法唔出聲<br />\n如果佢地係你身邊既人<br />\n麻煩叫佢地了解下咩係不合作運動先<br />\n<br />\n以下來自Wiki<br />\n不合作運動（英語：Non-cooperation movement），又稱非暴力不合作運動，是世界歷史上第一個全國性的非暴力反抗運動，由律師出身的印度國民大會黨領袖聖雄甘地。他發動和領導了1920&mdash;1922年和1930&mdash;1934年全國範圍的非暴力不合作運動。他要求印度人不納稅、不入公立學校、不到法庭、不入公職、不購買英貨，並多次絕食。<br />\n<br />\n不合作係你「自身」對政權既不合作<br />\n通過自身行為去喚醒民眾<br />\n跟住加入然後不段擴散<br />\n唔係迫其他市民同你一齊不合作<br />\n<br />\n車上面有男有女有老人有細路<br />\n有遊客有殘障有孕婦有病人<br />\n你咁做同啲白衣人有咩分別？"},{"pid":"d963d2e09d2c6c60aad6a58a1ea10abd7382e01e","tid":1358482,"uid":165246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3b4e7c908093a3785c56c2e5e61b04b4411ede53","tid":1358482,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:46:52.000Z","msg":"字眼唔需要執著，好聽就可以，好似請假係罷工，佔馬路係革命"},{"pid":"7cceb60b697e5b05e23bb017d4958d4e43e61f65","tid":1358482,"uid":35924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:48:19.000Z","msg":"仲推甘地出黎？google 下佢做過d 咩先啦"},{"pid":"60e04226b643e681e1da844bd24449047210dee2","tid":1358482,"uid":162783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:36:56.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"8c13f11fd32da87e5ea3ff4c276c7bec332f9d01","tid":1358482,"uid":78039,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:47:50.000Z","msg":"其實係真，被逼不合作係冇意思<br />\n咁唔會令基數大咗"},{"pid":"968440dc012ffaeb13411695e9c12b5290dc4013","tid":1358482,"uid":38668,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:10:53.000Z","msg":"我打工仔 被動罷工幾爽 義士請繼續不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689d71305feeec077104f5b6c5beeed0c29f713a","tid":1358482,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"0.3"}]}